      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DETANGLED (9) was in the money at Parkes two runs ago before finishing second at his latest appearance over 1660m there, beaten 11 metres. Will need an ounce of luck to slot in from this tricky draw but is good enough to put himself in the winners' stall. XCALIBUR (3) made a solid impact on debut seven-and-a-half weeks ago over 1740m at Bankstown, finishing third and beaten just 3.5 metres after taking charge of proceedings a fair way from home. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. His last-start form is good enough to put him right in the finish. WICKED STRIKE (2) faces the starter for the first time. By Mcwicked and hails from the Nathan Hurst stable. Was not far away in a recent trial and is likely to attract plenty of interest from punters. SING WITH ONE VOICE (4) lines up for the first time. By Always B Miki and hails from the L M Burns stable. Trial winner who looks above average.",
